short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Get reminded to practise your typing on vibetype.net

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is an extension for VibeType, a minimalist typing website. This extension has a customizable reminder to remind you to start typing.
Every amount of minutes that you choose, you will get a notification to practise your typing on the typing website vibetype.net.

Want more typing practise? Check out the main site (vibetype.net) for lots of extra stuff like multiplayer, leaderboards, and our discord.

Have fun typing!
